#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.23"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.23:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.23:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga "
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.23:0.3"
msgid "23. Parihānasutta "
msgstr "23. Decline "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.173, sc1
msgctxt "sn47.23:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca ānando āyasmā ca bhaddo pāṭaliputte viharanti kukkuṭārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the venerables Ānanda and Bhadda were staying at Pāṭaliputta, in the Chicken Monastery. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā bhaddo sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, Venerable Bhadda came out of retreat, went to Venerable Ānanda, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā bhaddo āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to Ānanda: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.23:1.4"
msgid "“ko nu kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena saddhammaparihānaṃ hoti? "
msgstr "“What’s the cause, Reverend Ānanda, what’s the reason why the true teaching declines? "

msgctxt "sn47.23:1.5"
msgid "Ko nu kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena saddhammaaparihānaṃ hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And what’s the cause, what’s the reason why the true teaching doesn’t decline?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.23:2.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, āvuso bhadda. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Reverend Bhadda! "

msgctxt "sn47.23:2.2"
msgid "Bhaddako kho te, āvuso bhadda, ummaṅgo, bhaddakaṃ paṭibhānaṃ, kalyāṇī paripucchā. "
msgstr "Your approach and articulation are excellent, and it’s a good question. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:2.3"
msgid "Evañhi tvaṃ, āvuso bhadda, pucchasi: "
msgstr "For you asked: "

msgctxt "sn47.23:2.4"
msgid "‘ko nu kho, āvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena saddhammaparihānaṃ hoti? "
msgstr "‘What’s the cause, what’s the reason why the true teaching declines? "

msgctxt "sn47.23:2.5"
msgid "Ko panāvuso ānanda, hetu, ko paccayo yena saddhammaaparihānaṃ hotī’”ti? "
msgstr "And what’s the cause, what’s the reason why the true teaching doesn’t decline?’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.23:2.6"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti. "
msgstr "“Yes, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.23:2.7"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā saddhammaparihānaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "“It’s because of not developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness meditation that the true teaching declines. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:2.8"
msgid "Catunnañca kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā saddhammaaparihānaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "It’s because of developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t decline. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn47.23:3.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.2"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā saddhammaparihānaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "It’s because of not developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that the true teaching declines. "

msgctxt "sn47.23:3.7"
msgid "Imesañca kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā saddhammaaparihānaṃ hotī”ti. "
msgstr "And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t decline.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.23:3.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

